---
import LayoutBare from "../layouts/LayoutBare.astro";
import "../styles/v3-sunset.css";
---

<LayoutBare
  title="Terms & Conditions · Jetski Lefkada Rentals"
  description="Terms and conditions for renting a jetski with Jetski Lefkada Rentals."
>
  <div class="v3 min-h-screen py-32 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <a href="/" class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] flex items-center gap-2 mb-12" style="color: var(--v3-flame-500);">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
        Back
      </a>

      <div class="v3-eyebrow mb-6"><span>Legal</span></div>
      <h1 class="v3-display text-5xl lg:text-7xl mb-4"><em>Terms &amp; Conditions.</em></h1>
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] mb-16" style="color: var(--v3-peach-300);">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255,230,212,0.8);">
        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">1. Eligibility</h2>
          <p>Riders must be 18 years or older and present a valid government-issued photo ID at pickup. No boat license is required under Greek maritime law when operating under our supervision.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">2. Booking & Payment</h2>
          <p>Bookings are confirmed upon receipt of a 30% deposit or full payment. Accepted payment methods: credit/debit cards, Apple Pay, Google Pay, PayPal. Booking confirmation is sent via WhatsApp/email within 2 hours.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">3. Cancellation Policy</h2>
          <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
            <li style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">✓ <strong>48+ hours before</strong>: Full refund</li>
            <li style="color: var(--v3-peach-300);">→ <strong>24–48 hours before</strong>: 50% refund</li>
            <li style="color: rgba(255,230,212,0.5);">✗ <strong>Under 24 hours</strong>: No refund (unless weather-cancelled)</li>
            <li style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">✓ <strong>Weather cancellation</strong>: Full refund or free reschedule</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">4. Insurance & Liability</h2>
          <p>All rentals include third-party liability insurance up to €700,000 per Greek Law 4926/2022. Personal accident insurance is not included and is recommended separately. Renter is liable for damage caused by reckless or negligent operation.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">5. Operating Rules</h2>
          <p>All riders must follow Greek Coast Guard regulations: maximum 700 metres from shore, no entry into designated swimming zones, no operating under the influence of alcohol or drugs. Violations may result in immediate termination of rental without refund.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">6. Weather Policy</h2>
          <p>Operations are suspended when wind exceeds Beaufort 5 as required by Greek maritime law. In such cases, a full refund or free reschedule will be offered.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">7. Damage & Waiver</h2>
          <p>An electronic damage waiver must be signed at pickup. Normal wear is covered by our maintenance. Damage resulting from misuse, collision, or rule violations is the renter's responsibility.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="v3-display text-2xl mb-4" style="color: var(--v3-peach-100);">8. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These terms are governed by Greek law. Any disputes shall be subject to the jurisdiction of the courts of Lefkada, Greece.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</LayoutBare>
